column5: Rain rain dont go away, bring those fires down and those fish up. Thinking positive.
Canoeing the Moon River this weekend.  Hoping for some high water so I can drag over some shallows and not have to portage!!
portage! Bad word for a old guy tooner. LOL Nice to hear from ya Nick.
bring those fires down those fish up. ? too early - give us a bit longer on the lakes yet.
I don't even wanna know how blown the local river is going to be after that rain, lol.
It will prob be wider than a mile by now! ?
